OL,3,CBoy drowned in Greek holiday pool
OL,4,Cafter unlocking apartment door,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FA five-year-old child drowned in a
OL,8,Fswimming pool during a family holiday
OL,9,Fto Greece after being able to unlock
OL,10,Fthe apartment doors, an inquest has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FTheo Treharne-Jones died after being
OL,14,Ffound in an outdoor pool at Atlantica
OL,15,FHoliday Village in Kos in June 2019.
OL,17,FTheo, from Merthyr Tydfil, was on
OL,18,Fholiday with his parents Richard and
OL,19,FNina, siblings and extended family
OL,20,Fwhen he died, South Wales Central
OL,21,FCoroner's Court heard.
