OL,7,FNina Treharne told the hearing the
OL,8,Ffamily had stayed at the same hotel
OL,9,Fthe previous year, albeit in different
OL,10,Fapartments, and those had door chains
OL,11,Finside the rooms to prevent children
OL,12,Fleaving.
OL,14,FBut this apartment did not have chains
OL,15,Ffitted to the door, she told the
OL,16,Fhearing in Pontypridd.
