OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FMs Treharne said Theo had been
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with the neurodevelopmental
OL,9,Fdisorder Smith-Magenis syndrome, which
OL,10,Faffected his sleep and left him non-
OL,11,Fverbal.
OL,13,FShe said her son could not swim but
OL,14,Fthey would as a family use the
OL,15,Fresort's splash pad, and he would wear
OL,16,Farm bands.
OL,18,FThe inquest heard it was late at night
OL,19,Fwhen they arrived at the complex and
OL,20,Fcollected their keys from reception
OL,21,Fand went to their apartment.
