OL,3,CBoy drowned in Greek holiday pool
OL,4,Cafter unlocking apartment door,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,F"I said to Richard there's no chain on
OL,8,Fthis door, you can't lock it, you
OL,9,Fcouldn't lock it from the inside," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"We had the prams and our cases, so I
OL,13,Fjust put them in front of the door."
OL,15,FMs Treharne said she woke up on the
OL,16,Fmorning of June 15 to hear a noise
OL,17,Fcoming from outside.
