OL,3,CBoy drowned in Greek holiday pool
OL,4,Cafter unlocking apartment door,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,F"I remember opening my eyes in the
OL,8,Fmorning and all I could hear was
OL,9,Fbanging and a woman shouting, 'There's
OL,10,Fa child in the pool, there's a child
OL,11,Fin the pool'.
OL,13,F"Our room door was ajar, and I went
OL,14,Fdown the stairs. I just remember Theo
OL,15,Fwas not in the room."
OL,17,FShe added: "He would never, ever be
OL,18,Fallowed anywhere near a pool by
OL,19,Fhimself. It was a case of waking up to
OL,20,Fan absolute nightmare."
