OL,3,CBoy drowned in Greek holiday pool
OL,4,Cafter unlocking apartment door,
OL,5,Cinquest hears
OL,7,FAnother holidaymaker saw Theo pushing
OL,8,Fhis buggy on his own but then saw a
OL,9,Fwoman near the pool and assumed that
OL,10,Fwas his mother.
OL,12,FOwen Sampson said: "I didn't want to
OL,13,Fget anywhere near him because if it
OL,14,Fwas my child and I saw a strange
OL,15,Fbloke, but I didn't want to, because
OL,16,Fhe was on his own... I was like,
OL,17,Fwhere's your mum and dad? When I got
OL,18,Fdown to the bottom of the pool, I saw
OL,19,Fa lady in a yellow bikini doing her
OL,20,Fhair and I just assumed that was his
OL,21,Fmum.
