OL,7,F"So I walked straight past and carried
OL,8,Fon."
OL,10,FThe inquest heard that another
OL,11,Fholidaymaker saw Theo in the shallow
OL,12,Fend of the pool and pulled him out.
OL,14,FResort staff and other holidaymakers
OL,15,Fcarried out CPR and Theo was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital by ambulance but later died.
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
